---
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
Description: >-
  Template deploy a Clickstream Analytics Solution that Integrates Amazon Kinesis Firehose, Kinesis Analytics, S3, Redshift and Amazon Elasticsearch in existing VPC.
Metadata:
